HEADWORD: Conchifera
<hw>Con*chif"e*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. L. <ets>concha</ets> + <ets>ferre</ets> to bear.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>That class of Mollusca which includes the
bivalve shells; the Lamellibranchiata. See <er>Mollusca</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conchiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
